<h2>The Cart</h2>
<p>The Cart can be accessed from anywhere using:</p>
<pre>
&lt;% if Cart %&gt;
	&lt;% with Cart %&gt;
		//do cart stuff here
	&lt;% end_with %&gt;
&lt;% else %&gt;
	&lt;p&gt;No cart was found!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;% end_if %&gt;
</pre>

<% if Cart %>
	<% with Cart %>

	<% end_with %>
<% else %>
<p>No cart was found!</p>
<% end_if %>


<h2>Ecommerce Configurations</h2>
<p>
